%h3
  Instructions

  %p
    Follow these steps to install the automation agent on instance XXX

  %ol
    %li
      Copy the below script to the clipboard.

    %li
      Log in into the instance and paste the script as super user.
      -#= @ip

  %pre
    = preserve do
      :escaped
        curl --create-dirs -o /opt/arc/arc http://localhost:8080/builds/latest/arc/linux/amd64
        chmod +x /opt/arc/arc
        /opt/arc/arc init --endpoint tls://localhost:8883 --update-uri http://localhost:8080/updates --registration-url

